| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2502 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit5)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9a66911a-464f-5d1c-baf6-29c493c4f6e8"
